info.author: Jamie Turner
info.description:
Py-SmugMug enables easy development of SmugMug-connected applications 
in Python.

It encapsulates the specifics of the protocol into a client class
which automatically manages sessions and transparently provides 
access to all SmugMug API methods.
info.name: py-smugmug
info.summary: A library for using the SmugMug API
info.html_description:
Py-SmugMug enables easy development of SmugMug-connected applications in Python.

It encapsulates the specifics of the protocol into a client class which automatically manages sessions and transparently provides access to all SmugMug API methods.
